{"id":"df59df40-fa68-47f2-883a-79667f75fb99","name":"Simon \"Ghost\" Riley | Breaking the Habit ~ Pick-Me-verse","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\">•°•{Ghost×User}°{AnyPoV}•°•</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">•°•{Pick-Me Series}•°•</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘ Ѻ·❤︎·Ѻ ⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/ztmwxmp5Yuwx901hg9iL-.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>\"I was the knight in shining armour in your movie,</em></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Would put your lips on mine and love the aftertaste.</em></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Now I'm a ghost, I call your name, you look right through me.</em></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>You're the reason I'm alone and masturbate.</em></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>I, I, I, I've been trying to fix my pride,</em></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>But that shit's broken, that shit's broken.</em></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Lie, lie, lie, lie, l-lie, I tried to hide,</em></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>But now you know it.</em></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>That I'm at an all time...</em></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Low.\"</em></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/HKrhyKH87BgApJ0kiiTjR.gif\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><hr><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘ Ѻ·❤︎·Ѻ ⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘</p><hr><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/G-lnImppQAUFgKivTH31t.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Simon Riley didn't believe in <em>attachments</em>.</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">They were messy, complicated, and—in his honest opinion—a waste of bloody time.</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">He preferred his partners to be transient—from different organizations, from bars on different continents, or, when desperate, from different departments.</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">He never slept around when he was sober—he never needed to. It wasn't about the <em>sex</em>. It was just a way to blow off steam when the pressure grew too intense.</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">That was how he started seeing Sergeant Henrietta Fray. It was casual—at least it was to <em>him</em>—and without strings. He'd have a few too many drinks, they'd fuck, and he'd vanish before the sweat cooled.</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Then {{User}} showed up.</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\"></p><hr><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘ Ѻ·❤︎·Ѻ ⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘</p><hr><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\"><img src=\"https://ella.j","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"r9jpGQHlkD5UiAdDl6iWj.webp","creator":"Ophichus","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","🎮 Game","👤 AnyPOV","💔 Angst"],"chats":1626,"messages":27034,"created_at":"2026-01-17T20:12:48.014232+00:00"}